data.fullDescription:
A spacious four-bedroom property spread over three floors with a private garden and off-street parking.
Coming to the market in great condition, this well maintained four-bedroom property is an ideal family home with off street parking and a large private garden. The ground floor is the perfect living space consisting of a spacious reception room towards the front of the property, with box bay windows that allow natural light to flood the interior. Also on this floor is the open plan kitchen/dining area. The kitchen comes fully fitted with plenty of storage and a breakfast bar, and the bi-fold doors direct you from here towards the private garden with natural foliage and partial decking. The second floor accommodates two double bedrooms, a third bedroom ideal for children or as a study and the family bathroom. Located in the loft is the remaining double bedroom which comes complete with an en-suite. The catio will be removed upon completion.

Avoca Road is a beautiful residential road that is situated a short walk from the wide open spaces of Tooting Bec Common. Tooting Bec Station (Northern Line, Zone 3) can be found a five minute walk away with local bus routes close by, both allowing easy access into and out of the City.

Tenure: Freehold
Council Tax Band: E

Information contained within this listing is for guidance only and should be checked and confirmed (prior to proceeding).

customerDescription.descriptionHTML:
MADE IN CHELSEA, IN 1856

From humble beginnings in the Royal Borough when London was home to just three million people, we are now one of London's longest-established and best-connected estate agents. With over 30 offices in prime locations throughout the Capital, we've placed ourselves at the heart of the community and can proudly say our knowledge and experience is unrivalled.

WE VALUE PROPERTY, BUT WE VALUE PEOPLE FIRST

This heritage means we've had a long time to get it right: we've continuously refined our way of doing business. Over the years we have developed a reputation for achieving great results for our clients using our intimate local know-how, highly effective open office network and the strength of our people.

EVERY PROPERTY IS UNIQUE. SO ARE YOU

The people who gravitate to one area or another are distinctive too: different priorities, backgrounds, age groups, nationalities, careers and day-to-day needs. Every one is unique. We take the time, and have the experience, to match people to a property that's right for them.

CONTACT US

We are available 8am to 8pm 7 days a week. Whether you are planning a move or looking for a valuation, get in touch.
